When creating an encounter note, you have to choose a Program from a drop down list. 
Once encounters are entered with a particular Program, that entry in the drop down is permanently present and cannot be removed.

You can use Ublock's filtering mechanics to hide unused program types.
  
For ublock lite:

Click the icon, then the gear, custom filters, Import/Export. Paste in: 

<yoursubdomain>.patagoniaemr.com##option[value="77386329-0c2a-45b5-8531-6d0e3847f1be"]
